{"id": 5873, "title": "Ticket #5873: condor_submit should not insert windows OSVERSIONINFO by default", "description": "<blockquote>\ncondor_submit should not publish the windows OSVERSIONINFO attributes into each job by default.\n\n<p>The following attributes will no longer be published into every job submitted from windows by default.\n\n</p><p></p><pre>    WindowsMajorVersion\n    WindowsMinorVersion\n    WindowsBuildNumber\n    WindowsServicePackMajorVersion\n    WindowsServicePackMinorVersion\n    WindowsProductType\n</pre>\n\n<p>A new knob will be added to allow for this behaviour to be optionally enabled (in case anyone cares...)\n\n</p><p></p><pre>    SUBMIT_PUBLISH_WINDOWS_OSVERSIONINFO\n</pre>\n\n<p>This knob will default to false.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Sep-20 14:03</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/9381dafb372dc1dd5ed089c732b481d14e9ea746\">[49242]</a></span>: version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5871\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5871'); return false;\" title=\"Remove obsolete knobs from param table before 8.6 release\">#5871</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5873\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5873'); return false;\" title=\"condor_submit should not insert windows OSVERSIONINFO by default\">#5873</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5818\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5818'); return false;\" tit